  <brief_title>Healthy Volunteer Study of Sildenafil Effects Upon Vision</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomised, Placebo Controlled Healthy Volunteer Study to Investigate the Nature and Origin of the Disturbance of Vision Induced by Single Oral Doses of Sildenafil</official_title>
  <sponsors>
