  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients sometimes report subjective visual effects when taking sildenafil. Our study set out
      to measure these in a controlled setting. Subjects were asked to detect patterns presented on
      a monitor screen.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
